## ğŸ—ƒï¸ Data Source

All data is pulled from **PMWare CMMS** labor reports:

| Month | Range | Status |
|-------|-------|--------|
| January 2026 | 01/01 â€“ 01/31 | âœ… Full month |
| February 2026 | 01/01 â€“ 02/20 | âš ï¸ Partial month |

Data is hardcoded into `index.html`. To update for a new reporting period:

1. Export a labor report from PMWare
2. Open `index.html` in any text editor
3. Find and update the relevant stat values, Top 10 tables, shift hours, and ticker items
4. Commit and push

